elements.title: Samuel C. Phillips (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that Wernher von Braun claimed that General Samuel C. Phillips (pictured) was the man most responsible for putting the pieces of the Apollo program together and making them work?

elements.title: La Folia Barockorchester (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that when La Folia Barockorchester made the first recordings of anonymous violin concertos found in the Dresden Hofkirche, they chose not to discover the identity of the composers?

elements.title: Stauffer, Oregon (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that in 1943, the United States Army conducted a large-scale battle near Stauffer, Oregon, as part of the Oregon Maneuver training exercise preparing troops for combat in World War II?

elements.title: Susan Chitty (Wikipedia — did you know?)

elements.title: Homalanthus nutans (Wikipedia — did you know?)

elements.title: Denise Jones Ennett (Wikipedia — did you know?)
